casino pass.

\C[3] Stolen Pass quest, if you use the obtained
pass here, the quest will fail. Is that okay?

\C[9]★Jackal's Fun Game Zone★\C[2] The only place
where you can enjoy high-rate, high-return JP! If
you want to live a winning life, you'll need
courage too! Now, let's have fun!
\C[3]※Underground Casino Pass is required.
\C[9]★Everyone's Fun Game Center★ \C[2] Enjoy exciting JP at high rates!\C[0]

Hey, hey, don't interfere with my business. You
must already have a master, right?

Hey, hey, don't interfere with my business! You
haven't been caught, right?

We've got a new unmarked girl here~ She's been
trained until she obeys everything. Whether
they're pregnant or not, all of them are obedient.
It's a great deal~
Hehe... You can't resist either, huh...

I heard you can buy slaves directly here, but it
seems like only the rich can afford it... Damn it,
I wish I could do whatever I want...

Hoho... How much are you worth... Hm? Aren't you a
slave... What a shame.

Today, it seems like there's an even wider variety
of things available. That despairing face... Just
being able to gaze at it here is the best.
変数25　竿の種類（0なし1スライム2触手3犬4人）
※汎用エッチありの場合はセルフBがONになるので注意

Your body is quite nice... but you might be a bit
too slim. I prefer someone with a plump figure,
you know.

It's so pitiful... I heard that once they are
branded with a slave mark, they can hardly escape.
Those girls will live their whole lives as slaves
once a buyer is found. If only I had the money...
ここでアイテムゲット
ピッキングで解錠する

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...

Konoha, who lost her magical girl powers, ended up
being sold in the slums.
I wonder if someone will take Konoha in...

In the trial version, you cannot proceed beyond
this point! You will not be sold as a slave, but
will be forcibly released.

We have a new unmarked girl here~ Whether they're
pregnant or not, all of them are obedient. Feel
free to train them as you please!

There's another cute girl today. If only I had the
money.

The man stopped in front of Konoha and carefully
examined every inch of her body, as if licking it
to assess its quality...
ジャッカル死亡の場合、結婚ENDへ直行可能
売春してない・売春追加エロに発展してない場合は振り分け1～10で抽選

Konoha, surprisingly, ended up being bought by a
wealthy noble. She was sold for a considerable
price, but as a condition, Konoha was required to
marry that noble...
Hmmm... You are... Konoha-chan...? No way...!?

Konoha ended up being bought by a wealthy noble
she had a match with at Alteano. She was sold for
a considerable price, but as a condition, Konoha
was required to marry that noble...
売春してない・売春追加エロに発展してない場合は振り分け1～10で抽選

Konoha ended up being bought by a wealthy noble.
She was sold for a considerable price, but as a
condition, Konoha was required to marry that
noble...
Mmm... You... are... Konoha-chan...? No way...!?

Konoha ended up being bought by a wealthy noble
she had a match with at Alteano. She was sold for
a considerable price, but as a condition, Konoha
was required to marry that noble...
Hmmm... The material doesn't seem bad.

Since she's top-notch... she'll come at a high
price, you know?

If it's just a little, it doesn't matter. As long
as we can earn that much...

Well, from today onwards, you will become Jackal-
sama's slave. Let's make sure you work hard...

\C[3] Konoha was sold to Jackal, who runs an
underground gambling operation. Jackal branded the
girl with a slave mark to ensure she couldn't
escape, and then set a target amount of money for
her to earn through relentless work.
バンディットの玩具へ（ヤリ部屋）

Hey hey hey... What's with this top-quality one,
huh?

Give me a discount, hehe... I want to fuck you
right now.

That girl is expensive... No discounts are
possible.

Huh? What are you saying? Should I spill the beans
to Mr. Jackal about that thing? I wonder how angry
Mr. Jackal would get, hmm? ???

Ah! I understand... I understand, so... 1000 Lo is
fine... Please, I'm begging you.

You should have said that from the beginning,
gyahhahahaha!

Konoha seems to have been bought cheaply by some
random bandits. If she had been lucky... she might
have been bought in a better way...
